article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- — Max Jones had 16 points in Cal State Fullerton's 67-56 win over Pacific on Wednesday night. Jones added six rebounds for the Titans (7-5). Dominic Brewton scored 15 points and added six rebounds. Grayson Carper finished 3 of 5 from 3-point range and 3 for 3 from the line to finish with 12 points, while adding eight rebounds. Moe Odum led the way for the Tigers (5-9) with 16 points, four assists and three steals. Nicquel Blake added 13 points for Pacific. In addition, Cam Denson had 11 points and 10 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
